title: Is We Dumb? | Snow Bank. Arby's. Monkey Suit. Stinky Balls.
description:
Have you ever imagined what the world would be like if animals joined forces and started revenge killing humans? Let's talk about that, the most insane doctors office of all time, trying to read a book while using a vibrator, mighty warriors riding miniature ponies, and more on today's episode of Is We Dumb?!

 

New episodes every Wednesday at 12pm PST
